             was indicted for <rs id="t18190915-42-off223" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18190915-42-off223" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190915-42-off223" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18190915-42-cd224" type="crimeDate">27th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190915-42-off223 t18190915-42-cd224"></join>, one pillow, value 1 s., and 3 lbs. of feathers, value 1 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18190915-42-victim386" type="victimName">
                     David 
                     Williams
                  <interp inst="t18190915-42-victim386" type="surname" value="Williams"></interp>
